6","parent":"201","text":"STOPP/START superiores a Beers en contexto europeo/latinoamericano","guid":"GEXR8Nz0J02CQP42pEtSnA","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"201","text":"Deprescribir es proceso continuo, no evento único","guid":"8rfBDc5F_EuKYSHDi1c-wQ","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"201","text":"Carga anticolinérgica → calcular con ACB/ARS en todo deterioro cognitivo","guid":"GgKusn7HakK6YC_ZLO4yow","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"201","text":"IACh + anticolinérgico → interacción frecuente y subestimada (contrasentido farmacológico)","guid":"i9q47afjUUiWh-u95O47AA","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"201","text":"50% hospitalizaciones por RAM son prevenibles → oportunidad de mejora","guid":"4XNxWdpbTUKGJwlBYXMUHQ","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"201","text":"Fragilidad y polifarmacia → relación bidireccional, abordar ambas","guid":"OCsUg9HI1UW948sBjDypWQ","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"201","text":"Al final de la vida → pasar de enfoque preventivo a sintomático","guid":"SxhO1MyvFE2ICHKRMmKuiw","children":[]}]},{"id":"213","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"PSiFA8CfKkyy2hqf9XU1fg","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"1. Arriagada L, et al. Polifarmacia y\\Ndeprescripción en personas mayores. Rev\\NMed Clin Condes. 2020;31(1):204-210.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"213","text":"2. Salech F, et al. Epidemiología del uso de\\Nmedicamentos en el adulto mayor. Rev Med Clin\\NCondes. 2016;27(5):660-670.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"213","text":"3. Gavilán-Moral E, et al. Ancianos frágiles\\Npolimedicados: ¿es la deprescripción la salida? Rev\\NEsp Geriatr Gerontol. 2012;47(4):162-167.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"213","text":"4. Delgado Silveira E, et al. Mejorando la\\Nprescripción de medicamentos en las personas\\Nmayores: criterios STOPP-START. Rev Esp\\NGeriatr Gerontol. 2015;50(2):89-96.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"213","text":"5. O'Mahony D, et al.